StoreWhereInput

Name Type Nullable
AND StoreWhereInput | StoreWhereInput[] No
OR StoreWhereInput[] No
NOT StoreWhereInput | StoreWhereInput[] No
id IntFilter | Int No
title StringFilter | String No
homeUrl StringFilter | String No
createdAt DateTimeFilter | DateTime No
updatedAt DateTimeFilter | DateTime No
pages PageListRelationFilter No
items ItemListRelationFilter No

StoreOrderByWithRelationInput

Name Type Nullable
id SortOrder No
title SortOrder No
homeUrl SortOrder No
createdAt SortOrder No
updatedAt SortOrder No
pages PageOrderByRelationAggregateInput No
items ItemOrderByRelationAggregateInput No

StoreWhereUniqueInput

Name Type Nullable
id Int No
title String No

StoreOrderByWithAggregationInput

Name Type Nullable
id SortOrder No
title SortOrder No
homeUrl SortOrder No
createdAt SortOrder No
updatedAt SortOrder No
_count StoreCountOrderByAggregateInput No
_avg StoreAvgOrderByAggregateInput No
_max StoreMaxOrderByAggregateInput No
_min StoreMinOrderByAggregateInput No
_sum StoreSumOrderByAggregateInput No

StoreScalarWhereWithAggregatesInput

Name Type Nullable
AND StoreScalarWhereWithAggregatesInput | StoreScalarWhereWithAggregatesInput[] No
OR StoreScalarWhereWithAggregatesInput[] No
NOT StoreScalarWhereWithAggregatesInput | StoreScalarWhereWithAggregatesInput[] No
id IntWithAggregatesFilter | Int No
title StringWithAggregatesFilter | String No
homeUrl StringWithAggregatesFilter | String No
createdAt DateTimeWithAggregatesFilter | DateTime No
updatedAt DateTimeWithAggregatesFilter | DateTime No

PageWhereInput

Name Type Nullable
AND PageWhereInput | PageWhereInput[] No
